            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-secondary mb-3" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/LuxuryWeddingsContent.astro:399p4o">Private Mountain Villa</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/LuxuryWeddingsContent.astro:gtbcgi">A secluded mountain retreat offering complete privacy, panoramic views of the Amalfi coast, and high-end concierge service.</p>
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-6" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/LuxuryWeddingsContent.astro:lay5p4">
