      <div class="space-y-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/LuxuryWeddingsContent.astro:lay5p0">
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-secondary" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/LuxuryWeddingsContent.astro:399p4n">What makes a wedding 'Luxury' with your company?</h3>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/LuxuryWeddingsContent.astro:gtbcgg">Our luxury weddings include exclusive-use venues, premium beverage packages, high-end floral design, and dedicated wedding coordinators to handle every intricate detail of your celebration.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-secondary" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/LuxuryWeddingsContent.astro:399p41">Can we customise the luxury packages?</h3>
